data.description: Opportunity Awaits! So many possibilities here with nearly 3/4 acre backing to BLM property. Veteran's Home? Bed & Breakfast? Care Home? Mixed Use?  This corner lot has many fruit & nut trees, a spacious workshop & beautiful forest views. The home was once a mixed use property with a doctor's office on the bottom level, and a family home on the 2nd & 3rd levels. There is a large eat-in country kitchen, breakfast bar, dining area, bedroom, full bath & living room on the main floor featuring a 2 sided wood-burning fireplace. Upstairs are 4 bedrooms including the owners suite as well as 2 full baths. The garage has been converted into a one bedroom apartment with a full bath including a walk-in tub, main living area, and space that can be used for a kitchenette. There is newly installed leased solar, a commercial grade furnace, county water, sewer & trash.
